value:
WITH languages, language_type, groupIds 
FOR e IN language_type 
    FOR gid in groupIds
        FILTER gid._key == "375608"
 
RETURN gid
name: playingedges

value:
WITH languages, ofLanguage, groupIds 
FOR gid IN groupIds
    FILTER gid.key.groupIdValue == @groupId
    FOR l IN 1..1 OUTBOUND gid ofLanguage
        FILTER l.value == @language
        RETURN gid
name: findGroupIdByKey

value:
WITH groupIds, ofGroupId, artifactIds
FOR aid in artifactIds
    FILTER aid.key.artifactIdValue == @artifactId
    FOR gid IN 1..1 OUTBOUND aid ofGroupId
        FILTER gid.key.groupIdValue == @groupId
            AND gid.key.language == @language
        RETURN aid
name: findArtifactIdByKey

value:
WITH ofLanguage, groupIds, artifactIds
FOR ofl IN ofLanguage
    FILTER ofl._to == @languageId
    AND ofl._from == @groupId
    RETURN ofl
name: findOfLanguageByVertexIds

value:
WITH ofLanguage, groupIds, artifactIds
FOR gid IN groupIds
    //FILTER gid._id == @id
    FOR l IN 1..1 OUTBOUND gid ofLanguage
    RETURN l
name: findOfLanguageByVertexValues

value:
WITH groupIds 
FOR gid IN groupIds
    FILTER gid._id == @id
    RETURN gid
name: getGroupIdById

value:
WITH artifactIds 
FOR aid IN artifactIds
    FILTER aid._id == @id
    RETURN aid
name: getArtifactIdById
